pageTitle: Family Fun Fest to be held tonight | TheAndersonNews.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {19164=The Anderson County school district will host its 11th Family Fun Fest on July 26 from 6-8 p.m. at the Anderson County Middle school. According to a press release from the school, the district plans to donate 800 backpacks again this year, filled with school supplies. If interested in donating school supplies, reserving a space for a business or making monetary donations toward Family Fun Fest, contact Beckey Johnson at beckey.johnson@anderson.kyschools.us., 24941=The Anderson News | circulation@theandersonnews.com | 502-839-6906 P.O. Box 410, 504 W. Broadway, Suite D, Lawrenceburg, KY 40342 Office Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, 33078=Copyright © 2015}
